    "Description": "Shared dictionary cache table. Read-heavy, shared across all users. One entry per word (lowercase-normalized). PK already encodes the normalized form: WORD#<word_lowercase>. Stores pronunciation audio S3 key, phonetic, and Vietnamese definition. TTL = 60 days from last update. No GSI needed — access only via GetItem(PK=WORD#word, SK=METADATA).",
    "AWSService": "Amazon DynamoDB",
    "Version": "3.0"
  },
